  target: FilterGenesScanpyOrder
  params:
    order:
    - min_counts
    - min_cells
    - max_counts
    - max_cells
    min_counts: 0.01
    max_counts: 0.99
    min_cells: 0.01
    max_cells: 0.99
- type: normalize
  target: NormalizeTotalLog1P
  params: {}
- type: filter.gene
  target: FilterGenesTopK
  params:
    num_genes: 3000
- type: feature.cell
  params:
    out: feature.cell
    log_level: INFO
    split_name: train
  target: WeightedFeaturePCA
- type: misc
  target: SetConfig
  params:
    config_dict:
      feature_channel: feature.cell
      label_channel: cell_type
